{
  "stem": "5430.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he another group arranged to bring my parents, and my sister, and my brother, Sam, and his fiancee, Shaindl.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To bring us back to Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sure enough, within a few days, they arrived over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all settled down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, my brother, Sam, got sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it wasn't the cholera-- a very serious disease.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he wound up in the hospital in Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And thank God, he got well, because of the good arrangements that we had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very, very Jewish organized community in Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when we got there, we all got organized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father started-- got a job in the restaurant in town, being that he was a restaurateur.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother, George, the oldest one being-- he was an electrician in his trade.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he got work right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my brother, Sam, who happens to be very artistic and-- well, a sign painter by trade-- but he also used to like to paint pictures.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember he painted a big portrait of Stalin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that way he got ingratiated in the political hierarchy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they gave him another-- also a job in the same restaurant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wound up going to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was a nice town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They sent me-- it was originally an ORT school-- a trade school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Operated by ORT, but then it was taken over by the government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was an auto mechanic school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were paying me money to go to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had a stipend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the reason for that is they needed auto mechanics in their collective farms.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
